	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				You can get the lore items from Najena or Cazic Thule.<BR>
<BR>
In Najena they used to drop rarely off any magician but I have been hunting there regularly for Mercury Drops for Smithing and have not seen them dropping there like they used to.  You can get them from the Goblin Magician however.<BR>
<BR>
In Cazic Thule you can get them regularly off the crocodiles.  If you are not high enough level, invis and get to the tunnel between the blue and green pools.  If there is a group hunting there (mostly there will be) ask them for the items you need.  While you are there also try to get a &quot;Ring of Evuluoy&quot; which the crocs drop.  This will be needed for the Circlet of Mist quest and you will want this circlet!
				</font>
			</td>

